irc2
====

* this is a client software for the Internet Relay Chat protocol including IRCv3 

* this program is written in Python standard library, please read and hack the code, it is very high-level and simple

* this program is for command line interfaces only (terminal emulator, multiplexer)

* this is a tool for investigating and handling IRC traffic on the raw, decoded and parsed level

* the client always does only one single TCP connection, if you want more connections: run more clients
